Create a lightweight domain event bus using Spring's ApplicationEvent infrastructure. This enables loose coupling between handlers (e.g., WH In confirmed → IQC created) without direct method calls.

Create:
1. platform/src/main/java/com/auraboot/module/meta/event/DomainEvent.java
```java
public abstract class DomainEvent extends ApplicationEvent {
    private final Long tenantId;
    private final Long recordId;
    private final String modelCode;
    private final Map<String, Object> payload;
    private final Instant occurredAt;

    protected DomainEvent(Object source, Long tenantId, Long recordId, String modelCode, Map<String, Object> payload) {
        super(source);
        this.tenantId = tenantId;
        this.recordId = recordId;
        this.modelCode = modelCode;
        this.payload = payload != null ? Map.copyOf(payload) : Map.of();
        this.occurredAt = Instant.now();
    }
    // getters
}
```

