@Component
@RequiredArgsConstructor
public class DomainEventPublisher {
    private final ApplicationEventPublisher eventPublisher;

    public void publishCommandCompleted(String commandCode, String operationType,
                                         Long tenantId, Long recordId, String modelCode,
                                         Map<String, Object> payload) {
        eventPublisher.publishEvent(
            new CommandCompletedEvent(this, tenantId, recordId, modelCode, payload, commandCode, operationType));
    }
}
```

4. Integration point: Inject DomainEventPublisher into the Command execution pipeline.
Find the appropriate place in the command execution flow (likely CommandExecutor or a post-execution phase) and publish a CommandCompletedEvent after successful command execution.

Look at: platform/src/main/java/com/auraboot/module/meta/command/ for the execution pipeline.
The event should be published AFTER the command succeeds but WITHIN the same transaction.

